<div class="lg:w-1/4">
    <div
        class="bg-[#081740] text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-t-md mb-4 text-center"
    >
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold tracking-widest uppercase">
            Announcement
        </h2>
    </div>

    <div
        class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg p-6 h-[400px] overflow-y-auto"
    >
        <article class="prose prose-slate prose-sm">
            <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase leading-snug">
                Youth for Peace | SKPF OF DAVAO DEL SUR PARTICIPATED IN THE
                INTERNATIONAL DAY OF PEACE 2024
            </h3>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-500 mt-2">September 21, 2024</p>

            <div class="mt-4 text-xs leading-relaxed text-slate-700 space-y-4">
                <p>
                    The Sangguniang Kabataan Provincial Federation of Davao del
                    Sur, under the leadership of
                    <strong
                        >SKPF President, Hon. Board Member Justin Siao</strong
                    >, participated in the event held recently in the capital.
                </p>

                <p>
                    This participation was made possible with the unwavering
                    support of our Governor, <strong
                        >Hon. Yvonne Roña Cagas</strong
                    >, whose commitment to youth development remains a top
                    priority for the province. The delegation focused on
                    peace-building initiatives and community-driven leadership
                    strategies.
                </p>

                <div class="bg-slate-50 p-3 border-l-2 border-[#081740]">
                    <p class="font-bold uppercase text-[10px] mb-1">
                        Upcoming Quick Updates:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-[11px]">
                        <li>Monthly Federation Meeting - Oct 5</li>
                        <li>Youth Leadership Summit Registration</li>
                        <li>Barangay SK Budget Deliberations</li>
                        <li>Sports Clinic Kickoff Ceremony</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <p>
                    During the summit, representatives from various
                    municipalities shared their local success stories,
                    emphasizing the role of the SK in fostering unity and
                    progress at the grassroots level.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Hon. Justin Siao highlighted that the federation will
                    continue to spearhead programs that bridge the gap between
                    policy and implementation, ensuring that every youth in
                    Davao del Sur feels the impact of the provincial
                    government's efforts.
                </p>

                <p>
                    Furthermore, the federation is preparing for the next
                    quarter's regional conference where Davao del Sur is
                    expected to present its "Project Basa Lingaw" as a benchmark
                    for literacy programs in the region.
                </p>

                <p class="italic text-slate-500">
                    Stay tuned for more updates regarding the upcoming
                    provincial activities and opportunities for local youth
                    leaders.
                </p>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</div>
